Class SoccerPlayer

java.lang.Object
Player
SoccerPlayer
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable
public class SoccerPlayer
extends Player
implements java.lang.Comparable
SoccerPlayer is a subclass of Player that is setup to hold values and methods for soccer plays who can be managed within a SoccerTeam class
